==English==
===Etymology===
Respelling of '''fishing''' <!--I presume-->

===Noun===
'''phishing''' (''uncountable'')

# (''computing'') The act of sending [[email]] that falsely claims to be from a legitimate financial organisation and requests the recipient to [[log in]] to a [[website]] and to supply confidential information such as bank account details, [[PIN]]s or [[password]]s; these details are then used by the owners of the website to conduct [[fraudulent]] [[transaction]]s.